The paper deals with the problem of spam SMS filtering using machine learning techniques. The focus is on the content of the messages, which suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) or Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of classifiers and vector representations also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Machine Learning (cs.LG).
